  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/System\/Errno\/improperLink\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T22:03:13Z\n---\n\n# improperLink\n\n**Type Property**\n\nImproper link.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstatic var improperLink: Errno { get }\n```\n\n## Discussion\n\nYou attempted to create a hard link to a file on another file system.\n\nThe corresponding C error is `EXDEV`.\n\n## File and Directory Errors\n\n- **attributeNotFound**: Attribute not found.\n- **badFileDescriptor**: Bad file descriptor.\n- **fileExists**: File exists.\n- **fileTooLarge**: The file is too large.\n- **isDirectory**: Is a directory.\n- **noLocks**: No locks available.\n- **noSuchFileOrDirectory**: No such file or directory.\n- **notDirectory**: Not a directory.\n- **permissionDenied**: Permission denied.\n- **textFileBusy**: Text file busy.\n\n",
